<a href="http://www.house.gov/judiciary/108-125.pdf#xml=http://wwws.house.gov/search97cgi/s97_cgi?action=View&VdkVgwKey=http%3A%2F%2Fwww%2Ehouse%2Egov%2Fjudiciary%2F108%2D125%2Epdf&doctype=xml&Collection=comms&QueryZip=1086&">Available here </a> </p>
              <p align="left" class="style2">  <em>Prior CSB article on 1086:  </em><br>
                <a href="/bulletins/apr03.php#featured">                http://www.consortiuminfo.org/bulletins/apr03.php#featured</a>  </p>
